{
  "stem": "3820.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Because even-- [SIGHS] even when the-- when the Russians liberated that part of Ukraine, the atmosphere for the Jews was not good.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when nobody knows you're Jewish, you hear a lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And Jude this, and Jude that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And my Uncle Sana, who was a hero and decorated and rescued, and went with the partisans all the way into the Carpathians, asked for permission to go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was denied.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we had to walk from Kiev to Lublin, hitchhiking on locomotives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because when my uncle went to Lublin to see if there were any survivors, he found a sister, a brother-in-law, and two daughters-- two of their daughters, two little girls.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he wanted permission to go back to live in Poland, because that's all the family that we thought we had left.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And from that point on, after hiding from the Germans and fighting with the Russians, he was in hiding from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he worked his way to Cyprus and to Israel before the-- before the Independence War, and got there in time to fight for independence in Israel.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "When I lived with him in Kiev, after the liberation, I did go to school-- to Russian school, and Ukrainian school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my mother did not come with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said goodbye to her in the forest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My Uncle Chaim and my father took me to the farmhouse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] She told me to be a good girl and to listen to the lady that was going to take care of me, and that she would try and see me as much as she could.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was in the farmhouse in hiding the rest of the day.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
